"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-olympic-venue-evacuated-fans-advised-go-home-21337906\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Fans have hit out at the decision to evacuate anOlympicvenue due to a weather warning in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 95, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 89, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999490683, \"rank\": 5.0914854610756424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ticket holders were able to enjoy the first Olympic hockey evening matches at the Yves-du-Manoir Stadium on Wednesday night before play was suspended during the later games.\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain were playing South Africa in the men's tournament while China taking on the Netherlands in the women's event when both matches had to be suspended and fans were told to leave.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995577574201231, \"rank\": 0.0004022671118553301, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9918002231027732, \"rank\": 0.006235263467271339, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999492943629811, \"rank\": 3.675711006169327e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 354, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7603982682899324, \"rank\": 0.3113055624163282, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A statement from the International Hockey Federation read: 'Following a warning from Meteo France of imminent storms, a decision has been taken by the venue and the local authorities to evacuate the stadium in the interests of public safety.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Hockey Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Hockey_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"score\": 0.9999999998469775, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meteo France\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The matches today are played as per the schedule.'\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Play resumed after the fans were removed from the venue, meaning the games were played behind closed doors in scenes reminiscent of Tokyo 2020, which imposed a complete ban on fans due to Covid-19.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991646665273, \"rank\": 8.353338538163406e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 are yet to confirm if ticket holders will be issued with refunds but several fans complained about the situation on social media.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.449821290222217e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The hockey has been suspended midway,' one wrote on X.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Spain v South Africa now playing for an empty stadium, with terrible communication from the officials.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995577574201231, \"rank\": 0.0004022671118553301, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9918002231027732, \"rank\": 0.006235263467271339, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I ask the organisers of Paris 2024 to issue refunds for me and all other ticket owners.'\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.449821290222217e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, another contactedThe Hockey Paperto slam the 'disgraceful' decision to send fans home.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When told that the 2nd session had been suspended we were incredulous - there was no sign of an imminent storm with no approaching lightning, thunder,' they said.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'There was general confusion and disbelief amongst fans.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have broken a 10 year old boy's heart - well done Paris 2024 and FIH!'\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1719, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.449821290222217e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once play resumed at the Yves-du-Manoir Stadium, Spain clinched a comfortable 3-0 win over South Africa in the men's event, while the Netherlands beat China by the same margin in the women's tournament.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995577574201231, \"rank\": 0.0004022671118553301, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9918002231027732, \"rank\": 0.006235263467271339, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7603982682899324, \"rank\": 0.3113055624163282, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999492943629811, \"rank\": 3.675711006169327e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But some fans were already on trains heading back into the centre of Paris by that point, with another ticket holder saying the feeling amongst fans was 'confusion and disbelief'  'What an absolute disgrace by the organising committee,' Dale Jackson told The Hockey Paper.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999490683, \"rank\": 5.0914854610756424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dale_Horvath\", \"score\": 0.9573853119201138, \"rank\": 0.04055545773558253, \"text\": \"Dale\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dale_Horvath\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dale_Horvath\"}, {\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999811513915249, \"rank\": 1.6888166080395772e-05, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My son and I flew all the way from South Africa to watch today's games and, in particular, South Africa vs Spain.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9918002231027732, \"rank\": 0.006235263467271339, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2311, \"end\": 2323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9918002231027732, \"rank\": 0.006235263467271339, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995577574201231, \"rank\": 0.0004022671118553301, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When told that the 2nd session had been suspended we were incredulous - there was no sign of an imminent storm with no approaching lightning or thunder.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was general confusion and disbelief amongst fans.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When we tried to query whether the session was merely being delayed and whether we should perhaps stay in the vicinity of the stadium, we were rudely told by security to evacuate and that we should check the ticketing app for further information.\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'At no stage were we given the option of remaining or watching the matches.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I checked the ticketing app and social media but no further communication was forthcoming.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was dismayed to read, whilst on the train back to Paris, that the match had indeed gone ahead - without any spectators in attendance.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3016, \"end\": 3021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999490683, \"rank\": 5.0914854610756424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A shockingly poor decision without any thought for fans who had travelled half way around the world, at great expense, for these matches.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have broken a 10 year old boy's heart - well done Paris 2024 and FIH!'\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3296, \"end\": 3306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.449821290222217e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Turkish shooter who went viral explains why he does not need any equipment  ArrowMO